<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2026 08:38:31 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>柯达数码相机</title><link>https://some.pics/69e49484b8e3f</link><description>&lt;p&gt;柯达数码相机&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="KODAK Digital Still Camera" height="3456" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dogsofparis/69e49484b8e3f.jpg" width="4608"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dogsofparis.some.pics"&gt;@dogsofparis&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2026 08:38:31 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>柯达数码相机</title><link>https://some.pics/69e493d774fec</link><description>&lt;p&gt;柯达数码相机&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="KODAK Digital Still Camera" height="3456" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dogsofparis/69e493d774fec.jpg" width="4608"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dogsofparis.some.pics"&gt;@dogsofparis&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2026 08:35:38 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>月之暗面独奏庆生</title><link>https://some.pics/69e47416afc06</link><description>&lt;p&gt;今晚在生日派对上演出——在《绿野仙踪》主题派对上独奏小提琴版《月之暗面》专辑（懂的都懂）。😋&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A photograph of a smiling woman wearing an intricate, turquoise-green patterned waistcoat with detailed tie closures over a white collared shirt, and a complex patterned scarf in purple and teal tones wrapped around her hair. In her right hand, she holds the neck and pegbox of a fiddle (violin). The background is a dense, stylized mix of textures including brown bark-like elements and tufts of soft, white unspun fiber or wool. A tattoo is visible on her right forearm at the bottom left of the frame.
" height="1117" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/sjwallin/69e47416afc06.jpg" width="858"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://sjwallin.some.pics"&gt;@sjwallin&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2026 06:20:09 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>木台上的鞋</title><link>https://some.pics/69e405828fa06</link><description>&lt;p&gt;两双鞋子摆放在日本戸塚区户外环境的木制平台上。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Two pairs of shoes on a wooden deck in an outdoor setting, 戸塚区, Japan." height="4032" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/rick/69e405828fa06.jpg" width="3024"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://rick.some.pics"&gt;@rick&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Apr 2026 22:28:22 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>机器人Alpha的永恒孤独</title><link>https://some.pics/69e3f279c009a</link><description>&lt;p&gt;我真的很喜欢《横滨购物纪行》漫画中的这一格。主角阿尔法小姐是一个一直独自生活的机器人。如今她与其他角色共度了这么多时光，他们却必须继续各自的人生旅程。她曾渴望独处，但现在她意识到自己也想成长。可悲的是，她永远不会变老，注定要看着他们渐渐老去……而自己却始终如一。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A black and white manga-style illustration of a person's face and shoulders. The person has large eyes and hair with bangs, and is wearing a light-colored top with a bow at the collar. A speech bubble on the left reads, &amp;quot;THERE ARE PARTS OF MY BRAIN I CAN'T MOVE BY MYSELF.&amp;quot; A speech bubble on the right reads, &amp;quot;HOW DO I PUT IT...&amp;quot; A small cup is partially visible at the bottom of the frame." height="496" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dawn/69e3f279c009a.png" width="628"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dawn.some.pics"&gt;@dawn&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Apr 2026 21:07:08 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>